name: Hippie Chic Bandana's
description:
Remember when you were a little girl and you folded a bandana and tied it behind your head to keep your hair out of your face? Well, be that little girl again with a "Hippie Chic Bandana"!

Yes, Hippie and Chic can be used to describe these 100 % cotton bandanas also known as kerchiefs. There are seven different designs of the Hippie Chic bandanas to choose from. They are perfect for any little girl, preteens to tweens to adults in your life. These are just in time for summer fun, picnics and parties. 

Pair a bandana with one of my posh petal tutus and your little princess will be delighted or rock the look of a ballet tutu. These bandanas are a cute reminder that style can be simple and still make a huge impact. Dressed up or down they are sure to make your outfit complete. 

The Hippie Chic Designs are as follows:

The Text It To Me Bandana
is Pictured in the Second Photo (girl on far left) it has a black background and has text graphics and a collection of cute and cool symbols and special text.

Polka Dot Strawberry Delight Bandana
has a white background with pink and white polka dot strawberries with lime green and orange flowers sprinkled about.

Peace, Love, Rock, Cool Bandana
has a pretty seafoam blue background with the words Peace, Love, Rock n Roll with some blue hearts sprinkled about. This bandana is shown in the second and third picture. 

Give Peace A Chance; Peace Signs Bandana
has a black background and is covered with Purple, Orange, Green, Pink and Blue Peace Signs(this item is not pictured).

Warm Skulls Bandana in Pretty Purple
has a Purple, Pink and Orange Tie Die background and is covered with White Skulls(this item is not pictured).

Tie Dye Peace Sign Bandana
has a Green Border and is covered with Orange, Purple, Green, Pink, White and Yellow peace signs in a Tie Die Look. This item is pictured alone in the first picture and is also shown in Pictures 2 and 3. This one is my favorite and it really stands out!

Lilly Rose Pink and White Bandana
has a Hot Pink border with a White background sprinkled with dainty pink roses. This bandana has a really cute shabby chic look to it(this item is not pictured).

***CAUTION: WEARING TUTUS AND CUTE ACCESSORIES MAY CAUSE EXTREME GIGGLING AND MAY MAKE YOU DANCE AROUND "TWIRLING BAREFOOT"...

name: "Tweet" Hat
description:
Spring and Summer are full of "tweet" baby birds & with this hat your baby is sure to be the "tweetest" little birdie out there! This hat is crocheted by me and has a cute tuft of "feathers" on top of the hat and a sweet flower adorns the hat. I can make this hat any color combination you like. You can choose yellow for a cute  baby chick, or have it made in pink for a definite girlie look. For the boys I love the blue/white combination with a pop of yellow added.

Since this hat has long braids added you shouldn't leave any child unattended with this item. If you wish to order this hat WITHOUT THE BRAIDS PLEASE NOTE THAT.
